Items.c: 妽兒,等事情解決了？是指兩國發生戰爭？還是指讓另一女子頂著公主名號代替我去遼國和親？
Items.mt: Yi Li-er, when things are settled? Do you mean a war between two countries? Or does it mean that another woman with the name of Princess will go to Khitan in my place to make peace?
